  #   DONE: 773 tests passing, 0 failures
  #   HARDENED (2026-04-01): fail-fast on missing key, 32-byte min, token size limit 16KB,
  #     nbf validation, ULID sub validation, case-insensitive Bearer, correlation IDs in logs,
  #     token bytes never logged, configurable expiry via JWT_EXPIRATION_MINUTES
  #   OPEN → T8: aud (audience) claim not enforced (cross-service replay risk)
  #   OPEN → T8: Token revocation not implemented (compromised tokens live until expiry)
  #   OPEN → T3: Dead user param in governance.py:list_governance_items (auth enforced but unused)
  #   OPEN → T3: Dead user params in strategies.py (4 endpoints use payload.user_id, not JWT identity)
