  # M29 COMPLETION SUMMARY (2026-04-06):
  #   All 8 acceptance criteria verified:
  #     AC-1: Complete approval flow via ApprovalsPage (TanStack Query mutations, cache invalidation).
  #     AC-2: SeparationGuard blocks submitter from approve/reject on own request.
  #     AC-3: OverrideRequestForm rejects empty evidence_link via Zod validation.
  #     AC-4: OverrideRequestForm rejects invalid URL evidence_link via Zod .url() + .refine().
  #     AC-5: OverrideViewer evidence link as clickable <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">.
  #     AC-6: Override watermark on all 5 surfaces: OverrideViewer, PromotionHistory, OverrideWatermarkBanner, RunReadinessPage, RunDetailView.
  #     AC-7: Approved override shows ACTIVE badge; rejected shows muted "revoked" label.
  #     AC-8: ApprovalsPage client-side status filter without page reload.
  #   Deliverables built:
  #     - Types: governance.ts (Zod schemas + TS types for all governance entities, 54 schema tests)
  #     - Errors: errors.ts (typed hierarchy with transient classification, 24 tests)
  #     - Logger: logger.ts (structured Sentry breadcrumbs for all lifecycle events)
  #     - API: api.ts (listApprovals, approve, reject, listOverrides, getOverride, requestOverride, listPromotions)
  #     - Utils: utils.ts (shared sanitizeUrl, 8 tests)
  #     - Constants: constants.ts (status badges, labels, filter options, retry config)
  #     - Components: SeparationGuard, ConfirmationModal, ApprovalDetail, ApprovalsPage, OverrideViewer,
  #       OverrideRequestForm, OverridesPage, PromotionHistory (96 governance-specific tests)
  #     - Pages: Approvals.tsx, Overrides.tsx (wired to feature components)
  #   Test counts: 1005 total (79 files), governance feature: 96 tests across 8 test files.
  #   Quality gates: tsc clean, prettier clean, vite build clean.
  #
  # M29 PRODUCTION HARDENING (2026-04-06, post-audit):
  #   Brutal-honesty audit identified 4 production gaps; all closed under TDD discipline.
  #   1. Governance api.ts imported raw `axios` — bypassed shared apiClient (auth token,
  #      base URL, 401 redirect). REWRITTEN to use `@/api/client` apiClient.
  #   2. CLAUDE.md §9 retry policy was documented but never implemented. NEW retry.ts
  #      helper (exponential backoff + symmetric jitter, AbortSignal-aware, injectable
  #      sleep test seam) with 19 unit tests. Wired into all idempotent GETs
  #      (listApprovals, listOverrides, getOverride, listPromotions). Mutations remain
  #      single-attempt (non-idempotent).
  #   3. api.ts had ZERO unit tests. NEW api.test.ts with 29 tests covering happy path,
  #      Zod validation failure (no retry), error classification (401/403/404/409/5xx/429),
  #      X-Correlation-Id header propagation, AbortSignal forwarding, retry-on-transient
  #      for GETs, no-retry for mutations, non-Error throwable safety net.
  #   4. apiClient request interceptor unconditionally OVERWROTE caller-supplied
  #      X-Correlation-Id headers. FIXED to honor incoming header (mixed/legacy casing
  #      tolerated) and only inject a fallback UUID when none provided — preserves §8
  #      distributed trace propagation from feature modules.
  #   Additional hardening:
  #     - Logger: added retryAttempt(attempt, delayMs, error, correlationId) for
  #       structured retry observability per §8.
  #     - Page components (ApprovalsPage, OverridesPage, PromotionHistory): TanStack
  #       Query queryFn now forwards `signal` to api.ts for clean cancellation on
  #       unmount / refetch.
  #     - Pages: Approvals.tsx and Overrides.tsx wrapped in <FeatureErrorBoundary> so
  #       render-time crashes degrade gracefully without taking down the shell.
  #     - normalizeError() helper wraps unknown non-Error throwables into
  #       GovernanceNetworkError so callers always receive a typed Error subclass.
  #   Files archived (per §1 Rule 6) before modification to .archive/ with 2026-04-06
  #   datetime: api.ts, logger.ts, ApprovalsPage.tsx, OverridesPage.tsx, PromotionHistory.tsx,
  #   client.ts.
  #   Final quality gate: tsc clean, ESLint clean, Prettier clean, vite build clean,
  #   1053/1053 tests passing across 81 test files (governance: 144 tests across 10 files).

